---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About the Digest"
	description="Web3 Digest — automated news on crypto, blockchain, and digital-asset regulation."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-03-30')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Web3 Digest is an automated digest of news on crypto markets, blockchain,
		and digital-asset regulation, including MiCA compliance. This blog collects, analyzes,
		and publishes reviews without manual involvement.
	</p>

	<p>
		The project was built as part of the <strong>Claude Code Basics</strong> course. Over
		eight sessions, the blog evolves from an empty template to a fully automated
		pipeline, where Claude Code finds news, writes articles, generates covers,
		and deploys to Vercel.
	</p>

	<h2>Editorial Policy</h2>

	<ul>
		<li><strong>Topics:</strong> crypto, blockchain, web3, DeFi, MiCA, developer tools.</li>
		<li><strong>Style:</strong> concise, informative, no marketing language.</li>
		<li><strong>Audience:</strong> developers and product managers.</li>
		<li><strong>Format:</strong> title, description (2-3 sentences), body (300-500 words), source link.</li>
	</ul>
</Layout>
